{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1995874, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 390493, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "如果本专业推研 不应该把较难的往后放 而是把给分差的往后放  如果转行 那当然不好刷分的都扔大四", "timestamp": 1625548121, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1995875, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 390493, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这是正常操作", "timestamp": 1625548122, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1995884, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 390493, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "得问教务，有的院系的一些必修课是保研之前必须上完的（除非交换不在学校）", "timestamp": 1625548168, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1995897, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 390493, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "可以但没必要", "timestamp": 1625548304, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1995934, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 390493, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "可以，当年室友就是这样操作。学分绩提高了不少", "timestamp": 1625548550, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1995958, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 390493, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "看来大家还是比较偏向可以这么做，dz可能还是觉得心里不太愿意，但有没那魄力，窝囊的很😭\n", "timestamp": 1625548740, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1995975, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 390493, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我们系推研之前未修的专业必修课不得多于1门，建议了解了解自己系的政策。", "timestamp": 1625548898, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1995997, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 390493, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "首先的确认这样操作的可能性，我们专业要求在保研之前必修课必须上完，如果你们专业没有这样的要求的话，那这样的选择完全ok，在规则允许的前提下让自己利益最大化并没有什么问题", "timestamp": 1625549209, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1996067, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 390493, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "常规操作", "timestamp": 1625550020, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 4, "pid": 390493, "reply": 9, "tag": null, "text": "求问，大家觉得为了保研把一些较难的必修课程放到大四修，这种行为合不合适？洞主现在很纠结，心底感觉这么做有悖于学习的初衷，但是又害怕自己学不好成绩下降，唉，心里堵得慌。", "timestamp": 1625548018, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1625550021, "url": "", "vote": {"vote_data": {"可以这么做": 105, "这样做不对": 39}, "vote_options": ["可以这么做", "这样做不对"]}}}